CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

November 30, 2010

[Cite as 11/30/2010 Case Announcements, 2010-Ohio-5806.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2009-2055. State ex rel. Brookwood Presbyterian Church v. Ohio Dept. of Edn.

In Mandamus. On S.Ct.Prac.R. 10.5 determination, cause dismissed as moot. See Brookwood Presbyterian Church v. Ohio Dept. of Edn., 127 Ohio St.3d 469, 2010-Ohio-5710, 940 N.E.2d 1256.

Brown, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, and Cupp, JJ., concur.
